## Communication protocol

Agents coordinate through files in `.agent/`:

- **Messages** (append-only): `.agent/messages/<agent>.md`
- **Status** (overwrite on invoke): `.agent/status/<agent>.md`
- **Backlog**: `.agent/backlog/tasks.md`
- **Heartbeat** (overwrite on check-in): `.agent/reports/heartbeat.md`

Message frontmatter:

```markdown
---
from: sender-agent-file
to: recipient-agent-file
date: 2026-01-01T00:00:00Z
subject: Short title
---
```

